name: birdhouse bracelet
description:
this little gold tone mixed chain birdy bracelet has a chunk of rough quartz attached to one side, it is followed by a little black round plastic bead & then a clear handmade glass bead that is strung onto the chain.  a black faceted cezch glass bead swings beside a little gold tone bird house. on the opposite side there is a champagne coloured sparkling swarovski disc. this bracelet closes with a lobster claw, the muted autumnal tones make this a perfect addition to any autumn/winter wardrobe.

measurements are as follows:
quartz piece 3cm x 2.5.
bracelet length approx 7" but has an extender chain, so can fit all sizes.

comes in a snappysausage drawstring pouch.

name: pirate bracelet
description:
the cute little pirate bracelet, made from mixed chain, gold plated curb & vintage rope style chain. a haematite anchor swings amongst faux pearls (white & grey), flat goldtoned disc, pink swarovski flower, little gold tone capped pink beads, a black bugle bead, flat black glass bead, smoky grey twisted transparent plastic bead, and a flat oval clear faceted bead. an oval plastic smooth black is strung where the gold plated curb chain meets the vintage rope style chain. bracelet ties together with a length of lace so you may need a little help doing it up!

measurements are as follows:
black bead 2cm x 1cm.
flat clear faceted bead 2cm x 2.5. 
haematite anchor 3.3 x 2.3 cm.
chain portion of bracelet 135cm or 5 1/4"
whole length of the bracelet 460cm or 18"
*this may seem like a lot, but baring in mind the lace is used to tie into a bow to secure the bracelet*


comes in a snappysausage drawstring pouch!

name: lil hamster earrings
description:
these cheeky little chappies are guaranteed to brighten up your day. ideal for casual wear & also a little bit fun for something a more formal! (that boring office party!) flash these beauties & you're guaranteed a smile!

they measure 2cm x 1.5cm approx, gold plated with a butterfly back, these earrings come in a handmade snappysausage drawstring pouch, making them ideal for a gift!

*made from my illustrations, therefore may vary slightly from the image shown, but supercute all the same!*

name: humpfry cat earrings
description:
these snooty little guys measure approx 2.5cm x 2cm (at their widest point) their little tails dangle down from the ears when worn, they are really cute & a bit different too. made from plastic with gold plated butterfly backs.

come in a snappysausage drawstring pouch so they are ideal for a gift!

*made from my illustrations, therefore may vary slightly from the image shown, but supercute all the same!*

name: she sells sea shells necklace
description:
this massive shell is on a super long gold toned ball chain. with a little black flower with little leaves attached, it's a super summery gift to brighten anyones wardrobe! a little white vintage lucite flower, cezch glass drop & faux pearls in two sizes meet in a cute little bunch.

measurements:

shell 5cm x 4.5cm
flower 2cm x 2cm
leaves 1cm x 0.9cm
flower 1cm x 0.5cm
chain 66cm (around) 33cm (hanging)
